# Resto

![Pasted image 20221104183003.png](data:image/png;base64,)

This element tracks:
![Pasted image 20221104183038.png](data:image/png;base64,)

But only for resto druid. I don’t think the bonus to healing is ever worth noting for the other specs.

---


Catform/Dash combined hotkey
```
#showtooltip
/cast [form:2] Dash; Cat Form
```

Taunt/Bear combined hotkey
```
#showtooltip
/cast [form:1] Growl; Bear Form
```


## These aren’t universally useful but decent models for same hotkey/multiple forms

I use same hotkey for ironfur/tiger’s fury
```
#showtooltip
/cast [form:1] Ironfur; Tiger's Fury
```

Same concept for balance druid, same hotkey for surge/ironfur
```
#showtooltip
/cast [form:1] Ironfur; Starsurge
```

And starfall/frenzied regen
```
#showtooltip
/cast [form:1] Frenzied Regeneration; Starfall
```

Instant NS regrowth
```
#showtooltip Regrowth
/cast Nature's Swiftness
/cast Regrowth
```

Cancelform/if no form go moonkin
```
#showtooltip
/cancelform
/cast [noform] Moonkin Form;
```
